creator: Dzing Finance Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Dzing is a multi-currency financial mobile service, «banking without a bank» for a global lifestyle. To get a UK account, all you need is a smartphone and a couple of minutes. Download the app, complete a short registration, open a GBP or EUR account within one minute, top-up your new bank account quickly and easily. You can order a Mastercard debit card delivered right to your doorstep, and get a virtual card to use both online and offline.

Discover a simple and modern way of doing your mobile banking.

Skip the bureaucracy
– Open your multi-currency account in minutes. Even if you don’t have a permanent address.

Get paid easier
– Accept global payments for your services onto your bank account.
– Large selection of currencies, transactions to/from any bank, in the shortest amount of time and with low commission.
– Receive money in seconds from your friends and relatives. No hidden commission.

Support your family
– A simple and convenient way to transfer money abroad with a low commission and absolutely free from one Dzing card to another.
– Fast card-to-card money transfer.

Buy whatever you want, wherever you want
– Pay for your online purchases conveniently using your Mastercard debit card.

Enjoy your travels
– Receive and transfer funds instantly during your trips. A useful option for unforeseen circumstances!
– Withdraw funds with minimum commissions – domestically or abroad.
– Check money exchange rates and access the currency converter.

Access your global digital wallet at any time, anywhere
– Get a snapshot of your total balance in different currencies across all of your current accounts.

From now on, you don’t have to worry about currency conversions – the sum will be displayed in any chosen currency whether it's Pounds (£), US dollars ($), Euro (€) or any other. This unique feature makes Dzing stand out among other banking apps in the UK.

Dzing is your complete online bank account and mobile payment app accessible with just one click. Access card-to-card payments, currency exchange, money compare, online payments and all this in multi-currency mode. Use your Mastercard debit card within the UK and abroad. Dzing card payment is available to you worldwide. Open a bank account online and enjoy the fast service!

It's your money, made simple

As a financial service, we guarantee fully protected and secure money transfers. All your funds are added to the Safeguard Account. Accessible only by you.
